title: The Partridge Family - Complete Season 4 [mp4]
description:
The Partridge Family Complete Season 4 

Suburban widow Shirley and her kids tour the country in a wildly painted bus performing music as a family. Their agent Reuben hates kids, so Danny gives him a bad time. 

Season 4 premiered on ABC from 1973-1974

This collection is a TVRIP so there is a station call sign in the bottom right hand corner of every episode.

720x480 (4:3) in MP4 formatte.
